  "text": "export umd namespace\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\r\ncurrent vue types export don't has export gloabl namespace.\r\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue@3.0.5/dist/vue.d.ts\r\n\r\n\r\n### What does the proposed API look like?\r\nlike this\r\nhttps://github.com/vuejs/vue/blob/dev/types/umd.d.ts#L48\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\n/// <reference path=\"./node_modules/vue/dist/vue.d.ts\" />\r\n\r\nVue. // this will trigger code completion\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n![捕获](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/521058/103499127-fd28f680-4e81-11eb-9d46-aca558833fb7.PNG)\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
